    PropertyNamesSelector

    public class TwoListSelector<T>
extends UIDialog
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.event.MouseListener
    This class provides a dialog with two lists for selecting objects from the left list to the right list. There are some buttons in between the two lists. These buttons can be used to move elements between the two lists.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
    See Also:
